4" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h1>
<p>Welcome to the comprehensive API documentation for the Corenet Tech Point of Sale Management System.</p>
<h2 class="group relative text-2xl font-bold flex items-center gap-[0.33em]" id="overview">Overview<a href="#overview" class="rounded text-[0.8em] text-muted-foreground p-0.5 -m-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 hover:text-primary hover:!opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200" aria-label="Link to overview"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h2>
<p>The Corenet Tech POS System provides a robust API for managing point of sale operations, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>User Management</li>
<li>Terminal Operations</li>
<li>Transaction Processing</li>
<li>Branch Management</li>
<li>Role-based Access Control</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="group relative text-2xl font-bold flex items-center gap-[0.33em]" id="base-url-and-authentication">Base URL and Authentication<a href="#base-url-and-authentication" class="rounded text-[0.8em] text-muted-foreground p-0.5 -m-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 hover:text-primary hover:!opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200" aria-label="Link to base-url-and-authentication"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h2>
<p>The API is hosted at <code class="font-mono border p-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-border/50 dark:bg-border/70 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] inline">http://193.123.83.134:8082</code>. All admin API endpoints are prefixed with <code class="font-mono border p-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-border/50 dark:bg-border/70 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] inline">/api/admin</code> and require admin authentication.</p>
<h3 class="group relative text-xl font-semibold flex items-center gap-[0.33em]" id="authentication-requirements">Authentication Requirements<a href="#authentication-requirements" class="rounded text-[0.8em] text-muted-foreground p-0.5 -m-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 hover:text-primary hover:!opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200" aria-label="Link to authentication-requirements"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Middleware</strong>: <code class="font-mono border p-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-border/50 dark:bg-border/70 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] inline">auth:admin</code></li>
<li><strong>Base URL</strong>: <code class="font-mono border p-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-border/50 dark:bg-border/70 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] inline">http://193.123.83.134:8082/api/admin</code></li>
<li><strong>Header Format</strong>: <code class="font-mono border p-1 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-border/50 dark:bg-border/70 [overflow-wrap:anywhere] inline">Authorization: Bearer {admin_token}</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="group relative text-2xl font-bold flex items-center gap-[0.33em]" id="core-features">Core Features<a href="#core-features" class="rounded text-[0.8em] text-muted-foreground p-0.5 -m-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 hover:text-primary hover:!opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200" aria-label="Link to core-features"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h2>
<p>Our API supports comprehensive management of:</p>
<h3 class="group relative text-xl font-semibold flex items-center gap-[0.33em]" id="-users--admins">👥 Users &amp; Admins<a href="#-users--admins" class="rounded text-[0.8em] text-muted-foreground p-0.5 -m-0.5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 hover:text-primary hover:!opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200" aria-label="Link to -users--admins"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link size-[0.75em] min-w-4 min-h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg></a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Complete user lifecycle management</li>
<li>Role-based permissions</li>
